VAR TodayDate = TODAY()
VAR LastYearDate = TodayDate - 365
VAR RemainingStock = [Ecom Stock Qty]
VAR DaysUntilStockRunsOut =
    COUNTROWS(
        FILTER(
            GENERATE(
                CALENDAR(LastYearDate, TodayDate),
                ADDCOLUMNS(
                    FILTER('Calendar', 'Calendar'[Calendar Date] = [Date]),
                    "@CurrentStock", RemainingStock - SUMX(FILTER('Ecom Sales Orders', 'Calendar'[Calendar Date] = [Date]), [Ecom Sales Orders Qty])
                )
            ),
            [@CurrentStock] <= 0
        )
    )
RETURN
    IF(
        RemainingStock <= 0,
        0,
        DaysUntilStockRunsOut
    )

VAR DateLY = DATE(YEAR(NOW()) - 1, MONTH(NOW()), DAY(NOW()))
VAR DesiredDate = DATE(YEAR(NOW()) - 1, MONTH(NOW()) + 2, DAY(NOW()))
VAR DesiredDatePO = DATE(YEAR(NOW()), MONTH(NOW()) + 2, DAY(NOW()))

RETURN
    IF (
        // Condition: If stock in 1 month is less than 0 and there are pending purchase orders (PO)
        ([Stock in 1 month 1] < 0) &&
        (CALCULATE(
            [Ecom PO Total Qty], 
            'Calendar ETA'[Calendar ETA] > TODAY(), 
            'Calendar ETA'[Calendar ETA] <= DesiredDatePO
        ) > 0),
        
        // Stock adjustment formula for the case where stock is low but incoming POs are expected
        [Ecom Stock Qty] -
        ((-[Stock in 1 month 1]) / 2) *
        // Add half of the lost sales last month
        [Ecom So quantity increase % last 180 days] -
        CALCULATE(
            [Ecom Sales Orders Qty],
            'Calendar'[Calendar Date] > DATE(YEAR(DesiredDate), MONTH(DesiredDate) - 1, DAY(DesiredDate)),
            'Calendar'[Calendar Date] <= DesiredDate
        ) +
        CALCULATE(
            [Ecom PO Total Qty],
            'Calendar ETA'[Calendar ETA] > TODAY(),
            'Calendar ETA'[Calendar ETA] <= DesiredDatePO
        ),
        
        // Stock adjustment formula for the case with normal stock and no issues
        [Ecom Stock Qty] -
        CALCULATE(
            [Ecom Sales Orders Qty],
            'Calendar'[Calendar Date] > DateLY,
            'Calendar'[Calendar Date] <= DesiredDate
        ) * [Ecom So quantity increase % last 180 days] +
        CALCULATE(
            [Ecom PO Total Qty],
            'Calendar ETA'[Calendar ETA] > TODAY(),
            'Calendar ETA'[Calendar ETA] <= DesiredDatePO
        )
    )

    CALCULATE(
        [SO Quantity],
        'Calendar Shipment Date'[Shipment Date] >= StartDate,
        'Calendar Shipment Date'[Shipment Date] <= TODAY()
    )

VAR ForecastQty = 
    CALCULATE(
        [Forecast Qty],
        'Calendar'[Calendar Date] >= StartDate,
        'Calendar'[Calendar Date] <= DesiredDate
    )

VAR OpenPOQty =

        [Open PO Qty],
        'Calendar Expected Receipt Date'[Expected Receipt Date] >= TODAY(),
        'Calendar Expected Receipt Date'[Expected Receipt Date] <= DesiredDate
    )

VAR StockAdjustment = 
    IF(
        ForecastQty > SalesCurrentMonth,
        [Available stock qty] - (ForecastQty - SalesCurrentMonth) + OpenPOQty,
        [Available stock qty] + OpenPOQty
    )

RETURN
IF(
    [Stock end of month] < 0,
    StockAdjustment - [Stock end of month],
    StockAdjustment
)

VAR StartDate = DATE(YEAR(TODAY()), MONTH(TODAY()), 1)
VAR DesiredDate = EOMONTH(TODAY(), 0)

VAR SalesCurrentMonth = 
    CALCULATE(
        [SO Quantity],
        'Calendar Shipment Date'[Shipment Date] >= StartDate,
        'Calendar Shipment Date'[Shipment Date] <= TODAY()
    )

VAR ForecastQty = 
    CALCULATE(
        [Forecast Qty],
        'Calendar'[Calendar Date] >= StartDate,
        'Calendar'[Calendar Date] <= DesiredDate
    )

VAR OpenPOQty = 
    CALCULATE(
        [Open PO Qty],
        'Calendar Expected Receipt Date'[Expected Receipt Date] >= TODAY(),
        'Calendar Expected Receipt Date'[Expected Receipt Date] <= DesiredDate
    )

VAR StockAdjustment = 
    IF(
        ForecastQty > SalesCurrentMonth,
        [Available stock qty] - (ForecastQty - SalesCurrentMonth) + OpenPOQty,
        [Available stock qty] + OpenPOQty
    )

RETURN

    StockAdjustment
